{"tid":1389821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民7月31 下午罷工","createTime":"2019-07-31T03:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T03:54:38.000Z","uid":274178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd7a9e64c9e0599b887f84cc36c7fa94a4cf4eb","tid":1389821,"uid":274178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"天助我地也！<br />\n<br />\n過去數小時，韋帕採取較偏北路徑移動。按照現時預測路徑，韋帕今日會逐漸靠近廣東西部沿岸，並於今日稍後最接近本港，在香港西南300公里左右掠過。預料下午本港風力會有所增強，天文台會在中午至下午二時考慮改發八號烈風或暴風信號。<br />\n<br />\nFact checked <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}